              </div>
              <div class="bg-amber-50 rounded-lg p-4 border border-amber-200">
                <h4 class="font-medium text-gray-900 mb-2">📦 No Storage Cost</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Generated images don't count against your upload bandwidth or storage limits</p>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-amber-50 rounded-lg p-4 border border-amber-200">
                <h4 class="font-medium text-gray-900 mb-2">🔗 Permanent Links</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Once saved, images get permanent URLs and can be shared just like uploaded images</p>
